# ── Development source — kept on local disk, NOT in the public distribution repo ─
# This repo publishes ONLY the Pocket distribution (Cores/ Assets/ Platforms/).
# The FPGA source and build/packaging scripts stay local and are never pushed.
src/
*.py
mister_source/
quartus_build.log

# ── Claude Code local tooling ─────────────────────────────────────────────────
.claude/

# ── Copyrighted ROMs — kept on local disk, NEVER committed ────────────────────
